Mrs. Smith's Kitchen

3
00:00:07,650 --> 00:00:13,770
Listen to the tape then answer this question.

4
00:00:13,770 --> 00:00:19,410
What colour is the electric cooker?

5
00:00:19,410 --> 00:00:25,020
Mrs. Smith's kitchen is small.

6
00:00:25,020 --> 00:00:30,980
There is a refrigerator in the kitchen.

7
00:00:30,980 --> 00:00:35,970
The refrigerator is white.

8
00:00:35,970 --> 00:00:40,030
It is on the right.

9
00:00:40,030 --> 00:00:45,520
There is an electric cooker in the kitchen.

10
00:00:45,520 --> 00:00:49,690
The cooker is blue.

11
00:00:49,690 --> 00:00:53,480
It is on the left.

12
00:00:53,480 --> 00:00:59,320
There is a table in the middle of the room.

13
00:00:59,320 --> 00:01:04,010
There is a bottle on the table.

14
00:01:04,010 --> 00:01:08,420
The bottle is empty.

15
00:01:08,420 --> 00:01:14,100
There is a cup on the table, too.

16
00:01:14,100 --> 00:01:15,100
The cup is clean.
